abstract:
- content: |-
    This Standard specifies an interface and services between two entities that request and provide communication services (e.g. Applications, middleware, PBX, IP-PBX, Softswitch, phone, softphone, software devices).
    CSTA operates with existing interfaces, so that differences among various existing interfaces are hidden.
    Services defined in this Standard allow functional integration between a computing network and a telecommunications network.
    This Standard is part of a suite of CSTA Standards and Technical Reports. SeeÂ documentation.
